<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 12px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to CondoMarket!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hi {{name}},</h2>
        <p>Welcome to CondoMarket - your trusted marketplace for condo communities!</p>
        <p>We're excited to have you join us. Here's what you can do:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Buy and sell items within your building</li>
          <li>Book services from trusted neighbors</li>
          <li>Connect with your community</li>
          <li>Build your reputation as a seller</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Get started by exploring listings in your building or creating your first listing!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 CondoMarket. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
